\/protocols\/cryopreservation\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">Cryopreservation protocol <\/span><\/a><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><span>Tanaka, Jocelyn Y., John R. Walsh, Kenneth R. Diller, Jerry J. Brand, Shanti J. Aggarwal,\u00a0Algae Permeability to Me2SO from \u22123 to 23\u00b0C, Cryobiology, Volume 42, Issue 4, 2001, Pages 286-300, ISSN 0011-2240, https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1006\/cryo.2001.2334 (<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.sciencedirect.com\/science\/article\/pii\/S001122400192334X\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">https:\/\/www.sciencedirect.com\/science\/article\/pii\/S001122400192334X<\/span><\/a><span>)<\/span><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><span>Taylor, R., Fletcher, R.L. Cryopreservation of eukaryotic algae \u2013 a review of methodologies.Journal of AppliedPhycology10,481\u2013501 (1998).<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1023\/A:1008094622412\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;:UNDERLINE;\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1023\/A:1008094622412<\/span><\/a><span style = \":;:;:UNDERLINE;:UNDERLINE;\">(<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/link.springer.com\/article\/10.1023\/A:1008094622412#citeas\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;:UNDERLINE;\">https:\/\/link.springer.com\/article\/10.1023\/A:1008094622412#citeas<\/span><\/a><span>)<\/span><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/utex.org\/pages\/cryopreservation#liquid\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">UTEX Culture Collection of Algae<\/span><\/a><span>, Cryopreservation protocol<\/span><\/li><li style = \"counter-reset:ol0;list-style-type:disc;\">Youn, J.Y. ,& Hur, S. B.( 2009). Cryopreserved Marine Microalgae Grown Using Different Freezing Methods. ALGAE, 24 (4) The Korean Society of Phycology. doi:10.4490\/ALGAE.2009.24.4.257<\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div>","changed_on":1620322902}